					No hidden fees, charges, or tips.
				</div>
				<div class="about_us_body">
					Nobody likes to be toyed with or treated like they're stupid. Yet every day that's exactly how most delivery services treat their customers.
					<p>After all, most restaurants that deliver will charge you a delivery fee, and might throw in a processing fee for good measure. (Seriously, does anybody know what
					the heck a "processing fee" is? If so, please let us know, because we don't, and we flat don't like 'em.)</p>
					<p>Then, after all that, when the driver shows up, you have to leave a tip. So that nice 6 dollar sandwich has just somehow grown into a 10 dollar sandwich, which is funny, because we're pretty sure
					you're getting the same sandwich that you thought you were when they told you it was 6 bucks.</p>
					With Littlejaw, there are no hidden fees, no delivery charges, and no tips. All costs are made clear and paid up front, so all you have to do
