		<div class="about_us_faq">
			Why can't I change my mind after 8am? What's so special about 8am?
		</div>
		<div class="about_us_faq_body">
			<p>In short, we do this to save you money.</p>
			<p>You might like having the ability to call up a delivery service on a moment's notice
			or the flexibility of being able to drive to the local deli for your lunch whenever you want, but you are paying a lot
			for that convenience.</p>
			<p>A typical restaurant has to be able to respond to unpredictable demand, spend an enormous amount of cash on the overhead associated with keeping a
			store open 12 or more hours a day, and keep a huge set of ingredients around to meet any request. Guess who ends up paying for all that?</p>
			<p>By offering a limited menu and gathering orders in advance, we strip all those costs out, and pass the savings onto you.</p>
